"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677483","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-01-27","<p>We do not routinely comment on specific capabilities as to do so would compromise operational security, and would, or would be likely to, prejudice the capability, effectiveness or security of the Armed Forces.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster","61197","2017-01-27T13:56:55.267Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677483/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677483/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677483/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-01-23","Royal Logistic Corps","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many Ammunition Technical Officers were in 11 EOD Regiment Royal Logistic Corps in each of the last five years.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","61200"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677484","Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","false","2017-01-31","<p>The minutes of the Ministerial Defence Growth Partnership (DGP) meetings are published on the DGP website. The minutes of the DGP Steering Committee are produced and owned by the DGP industry members and are not routinely published.</p><p>Departmental officials have sent your request to the DGP to consider whether they could release the minutes; they have requested that the DGP respond directly to the hon. Member and a copy of their letter will be placed in the Libraries of the House.</p>","Hereford and South Herefordshire","Jesse Norman",,"2017-01-31T15:03:45.207Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677484/answer","Biography information for Jesse Norman","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677484/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677484/answer",,,,,"201","Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","2017-01-23","Defence Growth Partnership","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy, pursuant to the Answer of 18 January 2017 to Question 60622, if he will place in the Library minutes from the 10 November 2016 meeting of the Steering Committee of the Defence Growth Partnership.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","61199"
