"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677486","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-01-31","<p>The cost of a test launch cannot be disaggregated from the overall cost of a Demonstration and Shakedown Operation (DASO). The 2016 DASO is estimated to have cost around £16 million.</p>","Sevenoaks","Sir Michael Fallon",,"2017-01-31T16:21:32.4Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677486/answer","Biography information for Sir Michael Fallon","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677486/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/677486/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-01-23","Trident Missiles: Testing","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what the average cost to his Department is of a test of Trident.","false","Biography information for Andrew Gwynne","Denton and Reddish","Andrew Gwynne","61186"
